s%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50GMELs.jpg&h=467fd33d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:12:40.000Z","msg":"每次見到班狗惱羞成怒，狗急跳牆都覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f7ed54658ba37ffecd515667bbcd923f8a6795","tid":1852094,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:19:17.000Z","msg":"好驚咩?你班狗放心喎 我中左實去狗屋同狗宿先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5937c592104ab4b7baa7fdf942494e5d9e675de","tid":1852094,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dc1aed0a9996641883f93ee1536e1ee2ebbc276","tid":1852094,"uid":170335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:59:49.000Z","msg":"講事實就煽動仇警？<br />\n即係事實就係咁犯眾憎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:23:43.000Z","msg":"問題係仇警<br />\n邊撚使煽動？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如同呼吸<br />\n係好乸正常嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32dfae0fcc6507bb8114d81aa14adf1b649c02b8","tid":1852094,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6e32c43c6b8295dd3dd8b4800dcf57047fcc8ac","tid":1852094,"uid":65178,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T10:01:55.000Z","msg":"我個人上會全力推廣仇恨黑警既概念<br />\n<br />\n無論黑警做乜都係有陰謀 唔會分析<br />\n無論黑警講乜都係大話 唔會分析<br />\n無論黑警有咩行動都係犯罪 唔會分析<br />\n無論黑警想做咩洗白都唔會原諒 只有死全家呢個結局 唔會分析<br />\n無論黑警係咪我自己既家屬 都會立即割席 我一齊死都無問題 唔會分析<br />\n無論係咩人支持黑警同情黑警都係我敵人 唔會分析<br />\n<br />\n我會慢慢提倡俾身邊人 教我既後代 再叫佢地宣揚出去 生生世世永不原諒港共黑警<br />\n落地獄啦你班仆街狗閪<br />\n<br />\n612 721 811 831 929 101 112 113 1111 1112 1117 1118 新屋嶺 還眼 還命 被自殺 實彈 周同學 陳同學 雞姦 強姦 輪姦 因姦成孕 中大理大之戰 人踩人 濫捕<br />\n<br />\n睇完呢串事件 連杯曱甴都做唔到嘅<br />\n唔好同人講你要光復香港 呢埋喺屋企訓教吧啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T12:24:53.000Z","msg":"推 無白警"}],"pinned":{"pid":"763992445c8bef9ec24cf13838be1afdbe56470b","tid":1852094,"uid":127929,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T09:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bJCoG2p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbJCoG2p.jpg&h=ebff6a32&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\npopo又點解釋張圖先, 反正我信左"}}